OL,3,CThe club helping women in their
OL,4,Ctwenties find friends after uni
OL,6,FOn an island of just 65,000, it's
OL,7,Fdifficult for many young people living
OL,8,Fin Guernsey to make new friends.
OL,10,FHowever, six months ago, friends
OL,11,FImogen Remfrey and Sophie Rabey,
OL,12,Fdecided to do something about it.
OL,14,FThey set up the 'Twenty Something
OL,15,FClub' to foster friendships between
OL,16,Fthose who may have seen their social
OL,17,Fcircle dissolve.
