OL,3,CThe club helping women in their
OL,4,Ctwenties find friends after uni
OL,6,FImogen said: "Coming back (from
OL,7,Funiversity) we had to rebuild our life
OL,8,Fand friendships. We found it to be
OL,9,Fsomething that was quite difficult to
OL,10,Fdo within your 20s unless you played a
OL,11,Fsport.
OL,13,F"I worked for a relatively small
OL,14,Fcompany so there were no opportunities
OL,15,Fwhere you could meet people so we
OL,16,Fthought if others are having those
OL,17,Ffeelings, it's likely others are too.
OL,19,FShe added: "This is our twelfth event
OL,20,Fso yeah, it's grown and we are so
OL,21,Fproud of what it's become."
