OL,3,CThe club helping women in their
OL,4,Ctwenties find friends after uni
OL,6,FThe group runs a variety of different
OL,7,Fsocials, from beach walks to arts and
OL,8,Fcrafts nights. Those who attend say
OL,9,Fit's allowed them to try activities
OL,10,Fand things they don't usually do.
OL,12,FEnya Rabey usually spends her weekends
OL,13,Fdoing something sporty. Since she
OL,14,Fjoined, Enya has tried a wealth of
OL,15,Factivities such as candle-making.
