OL,3,CThe club helping women in their
OL,4,Ctwenties find friends after uni
OL,6,FShe said: "It's encouraging people to
OL,7,Fmeet new people but also do things
OL,8,Fthat are a bit out of their comfort
OL,9,Fzone. It's definitely pushed me to do
OL,10,Fthings I wouldn't previously have
OL,11,Fdone."
OL,13,FIt's hoped the club-run activities can
OL,14,Fimprove girls' mental health across
OL,15,Fthe island. Enya says those in their
OL,16,Ftwenties suffer due to social media
OL,17,Fpressures that exist.
OL,19,FShe explains: "Social media can be an
OL,20,Famazing tool as it's connected all of
OL,21,Fus here.
